review_text: The East Hartford branch on Main Street is the best branch I've been too. They great you right away and the staff is always very positive. I used to go to the Stop n Shop branch in Manchester before it closed cuz Kelsey was such a great teller. Since them closing I've moved to East Hartford,  so this branch is also closest to me. Anyways, I just wanted to say how great everyone is at that particular Branch.
